in my report:

34:52.917 --> 34:55.375
"Victim had $1 million."

34:55.375 --> 34:57.250
It's 1.2.
Look.

34:57.250 --> 35:00.083
Please.
I'm telling you the truth.

35:00.083 --> 35:02.208
Yes, sir. We'll put
a dedicated task force on it.

35:02.208 --> 35:04.041
You're not fucking
listening to me!

35:04.041 --> 35:07.083
Sir.
You need to calm down.

35:07.083 --> 35:08.917
I'm sorry.

35:08.917 --> 35:10.250
Please.
You gotta help me.

35:10.250 --> 35:12.000
Sir, why don't you
go over to the ambulance,

35:12.000 --> 35:13.959
