35:43.792 --> 35:45.417
Chop-chop.

35:53.542 --> 35:55.500
[grunts]

35:57.458 --> 35:59.083
[water splashes]

36:03.583 --> 36:04.709
Let's go.

36:06.709 --> 36:08.583
[groans]

36:12.667 --> 36:13.917
[grunts]

36:15.625 --> 36:18.500
[grunts]

36:18.500 --> 36:20.375
[Mickey] I'll help you here.

36:21.542 --> 36:22.834
[chain clanking]

36:22.834 --> 36:23.959
[both grunt]

36:23.959 --> 36:24.500
I got it.

36:27.542 --> 36:30.000
All right,
one, two, three!

36:30.000 --> 36:33.125
[whooshing]

36:39.375 --> 36:41.166
Look at me.

36:43.625 --> 36:44.792
He was the professional,

36:44.792 --> 36:48.875
and he put this fucking
razor-sharp weapon in your hand.

36:48.875 --> 36:50.500
Whose fault is that?

36:50.500 --> 36:51.375
See?

36:54.166 --> 36:55.709
You got some kind of

36:55.709 --> 36:57.834
formal Jap good-bye
or something?

36:57.834 --> 36:59.250
You can do it now.

37:06.208 --> 37:08.250
[breathes shakily]

37:14.208 --> 37:16.083
