37:16.709 --> 37:18.750
[sniffles]

37:22.667 --> 37:24.375
[exhales, sniffles]

37:32.583 --> 37:34.834
All will be well.

37:34.834 --> 37:38.417
It's a great big ocean
and a very tiny sensei.

37:42.208 --> 37:43.375
Home is the hunter,
home from the hill,

37:43.375 --> 37:45.083
and the sailor home
from the sea.

37:45.083 --> 37:47.291
Let's get back to land.

37:47.291 --> 37:49.959
- [Mickey] Eh?
- [engine revs]

37:49.959 --> 37:53.125
[engine puttering]

37:54.834 --> 37:58.750
[engine revving]

38:02.959 --> 38:06.875
[doorbell chimes]

38:15.291 --> 38:17.125
Hey, Ray.

38:17.125 --> 38:19.250
What are you doing here?

38:19.250 --> 38:21.500
I gotta talk to you
about Sam Winslow.

38:22.959 --> 38:25.250
All right.

38:44.917 --> 38:47.166
[engine cuts out]

38:50.125 --> 38:51.583
Go get the security cam
footage.

38:54.250 --> 38:56.083
Hold up.
Hold up.

38:56.083 --> 38:59.750
Uh, I don't know
what arrangements you made

38:59.750 --> 39:01.000
with my son,

39:01.000 --> 39:03.834
but my services
aren't included.

39:03.834 --> 39:06.458
No?

39:06.458 --> 39:07.625
No.

39:07.625 --> 39:09.291
So what do I owe you?

39:11.291 --> 39:13.667
I've been getting
some excellent feedback

39:13.667 --> 39:17.250
on this little film
that I wrote.

39:17.250 --> 39:18.333
Four Leaf?

39:18.333 --> 39:20.166
Yeah, as in clover.

39:20.166 --> 39:22.208
And you and I know

39:22.208 --> 39:23.250
that, uh, nothing
gets made in this town

39:23.250 --> 39:25.834
without-without a star.

39:25.834 --> 39:28.834
Listen, Mr. Donovan,
this is not how things work.

39:28.834 --> 39:30.750
Look,

39:30.750 --> 39:32.959
The time to call your lawyer

39:32.959 --> 39:35.709
was before you called my son.

39:35.709 --> 39:37.750
We understand each other?

39:37.750 --> 39:39.333
[sucks teeth]

39:42.000 --> 39:43.208
We'll hold on to those.

39:43.208 --> 39:45.500
They'll be safe with us.

39:45.500 --> 39:49.208
I'll, uh...
I'll take care of, uh,

39:49.208 --> 39:50.375
Sensei's car.

39:50.375 --> 39:51.667
You can go.

39:54.750 --> 39:56.500
