43:15.709 --> 43:19.625
Damon is going out
to dinner tonight.

43:20.250 --> 43:22.750
With his father.

43:24.583 --> 43:26.125
His father?

43:26.125 --> 43:27.959
I didn't know
he was in the picture.

43:27.959 --> 43:30.000
Yeah.

43:30.000 --> 43:31.250
Me neither.

43:31.250 --> 43:34.166
Teresa's...

43:34.166 --> 43:37.750
out with the Crafty Fox.

43:37.750 --> 43:39.166
The what?

43:41.083 --> 43:43.250
El Zorro Astuto.

43:43.250 --> 43:46.500
It's another luchador.

43:46.500 --> 43:48.125
[soul music playing
over speakers]

43:48.125 --> 43:50.625
That's a shit name.

43:50.625 --> 43:53.625
♪♪♪

43:53.625 --> 43:57.125
I was El Trebol,

43:57.125 --> 43:58.417
The Shamrock.

43:58.417 --> 44:00.125
That's a better name.

44:00.125 --> 44:02.500
'Cept I ain't got no luck.

44:03.750 --> 44:05.166
Ah, me neither, Bunch.

44:05.166 --> 44:07.083
[door opens]

44:07.083 --> 44:08.083
Me neither.

44:08.083 --> 44:09.792
Two glasses, Bunch.

44:11.792 --> 44:14.125
Three of my four boys

44:14.125 --> 44:16.458
