Jay White.

44:28.625 --> 44:30.583
The "Check's in the mail" guy?

44:30.583 --> 44:32.750
None other.

44:32.750 --> 44:33.709
Jay White's black, Pop.

44:33.709 --> 44:37.000
This is the modern times,
Bunch.

44:37.000 --> 44:38.583
They can do all sorts of shit
with their computers.

44:38.583 --> 44:42.166
What the fuck
are you talking about?

44:42.166 --> 44:43.834
